Orders = folium.map.FeatureGroup()
for lat,lng,label, in zip(df_order.geolocation_lat,df_order.geolocation_lng,df_order.geolocation_state):
  Orders.add_child(
      folium.features.CircleMarker(
          [lat,lng],
          readius = 5,
          color = 'yellow',
          fill = True,
          fill_color = 'blue',
          fill_opacity = 0.6
      )
  )
  folium.Marker([lat,lng],popup=label).add_to(sanP_Map)
